summary: Direct go inside to the Ragged Flagon in Riften.
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5]
[color=#00ff00]Riften Ragged Flagon Entry

[/color][/size][/b][b][color=#ffff00][size=4]V1.1[/size][/color][/b]
[size=3]The Ragged Flagon entrance from outside behind the Riften Stable and Honeyside.[/size]
[b][color=#ff0000][size=3]Choose only one main file please.[/size][/color][/b]

[size=3]When doing Thieves Guild Special Job Quests, [/size]
[size=3]you must many times to go to the Ragged Flagon. [/size]
[size=3]But first you must go to the Cistern or to the Ratway.[/size]
[size=3]
[/size][size=3]You can direct go inside to the Ragged Flagon with this mod
if you don't prefer to use console commands.[/size][size=3]
[/size][size=3]After discovering, you can fast travel.Â
